{"tid":612884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google偷偷save你資料 10年前睇過咩片都知曉？","createTime":"2018-04-01T07:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T08:21:52.000Z","uid":53026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a9d87b78e8e18306c4e0bc96a379e87dc8df3a","tid":612884,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"Google偷偷save你資料<br />\n10年前睇過咩片都知曉？<br />\n<br />\nFacebook洩露約5,000萬用戶個人資料引起軒然大波，愛爾蘭瓦特福（Waterford）一名IT專家下載自己Facebook及Google資料檔案，驚訝地揭發Google保存的檔案較Facebook更多更廣泛。<br />\n<br />\n網頁開發者柯倫（Dylan Curran）決定在剛過去的周六，下載自己Facebook及Google資料檔案，前者約600mb，相當於大約40萬個Word檔案；後者約5.5gb，相當於大約300萬個Word檔案。Google保存的資料檔案，可追溯至2008年。到底Google保存了甚麼資料呢？<br />\n<br />\n你所到之處<br />\n假如你在手機、平板電腦或其他裝置開啟了位置追蹤功能，Google就會紀錄你所到之處、旅途所需時間、你到過的餐廳的名字、你在餐廳待了多久及回家路線等，小編也驚覺Google對我在香港的行蹤瞭如指掌，想知道掌握了你的甚麼資料，可看看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/timeline?pb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Ftimeline%3Fpb&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a7a1f491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/timeline?pb</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube瀏覽紀錄<br />\n以柯倫為倫，他自2008年起搜尋過或瀏覽過的每條YouTube影片，Google都一一紀錄，這兒你可看看自己的紀錄：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/feed/history/search_history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Ffeed%2Fhistory%2Fsearch_history&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e441e149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/feed/history/search_history</a><br />\n<br />\n你曾搜尋過的一切<br />\n即使你刪除瀏覽歷史，Google仍保存你的搜尋紀錄。以柯倫為例，他曾搜尋9萬次，想看看你下載過的圖片、瀏覽過的網站，Google有以下紀錄：<br />\n<a href=\"https://myactivity.google.com/myactivity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyactivity.google.com%2Fmyactivity&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0431fbb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myactivity.google.com/myactivity</a><br />\n<br />\n你拍過或搜尋過的所有照片<br />\n用手機拍過的每張照片，何時拍、那裡拍都一一紀錄。搜尋過或保存過的每張照片也不例外。<br />\n<a href=\"https://myactivity.google.com/myactivity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyactivity.google.com%2Fmyactivity&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0431fbb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myactivity.google.com/myactivity</a><br />\n<br />\n你出席過的活動<br />\nGoogle的資料檔案保存你月曆的完整紀錄，例如是你曾輸入的所有活動，根據你的位置來判斷你是否真的有出席，以及出席時間，按按以下連結就知道：<a href=\"https://takeout.google.com/settings/takeout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftakeout.google.com%2Fsettings%2Ftakeout&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f8aebed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://takeout.google.com/settings/takeout</a><br />\n<br />\n你刪除的資料及你發過的電郵<br />\n柯倫發現了他早已刪除的檔案、曾經收發過的電郵，包括已刪除電郵及垃圾電郵，有興趣可以找找看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://takeout.google.com/settings/takeout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftakeout.google.com%2Fsettings%2Ftakeout&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f8aebed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://takeout.google.com/settings/takeout</a><br />\n<br />\n你用過的應用程式<br />\n這包括你有多常用這些應用程式、在那裡用這些應用程式、你在這些應用程式上與誰交流過、交流對象身處那些國家，甚至是你的睡眠時間：<br />\n<a href=\"https://myaccount.google.com/permissions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyaccount.google.com%2Fpermissions&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a6c45803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myaccount.google.com/permissions</a><br />\n<br />\n你或有興趣的廣告話題<br />\nGoogle根據你的位置、性別及年齡，來建立市場推廣檔案。你的搜尋紀錄及網絡活動，都會透露你的嗜好及興趣。以柯倫為例，Google就推斷了他的感情狀況、體重及收入，可看看Google是否看破了你：<br />\n<a href=\"https://adssettings.google.com/authenticated\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadssettings.google.com%2Fauthenticated&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=dbde660e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://adssettings.google.com/authenticated</a><br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"31d702f64e46ef71d10cea4612870fad0a709d13","tid":612884,"uid":131323,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"出呢d新聞都幾撚無聊<br />\n講明大數據時代<br />\n唔收集呢d點分析同賺錢<br />\n難聽d講句google其實同wechat一樣<br />\n要收集你數據有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebb6eaf3fb9ecaeb28a60e7b16b39e7e72f95d8","tid":612884,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"其實上網個一刻已經走唔甩"},{"pid":"f823b3f74b40eeb7a71093c345e9566b7dc4e473","tid":612884,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"所以唔明d人成日話小米華為唔安全<br />\n用乜手機都死架啦"},{"pid":"a2492d89a4e652a1c25437e8ebf148d1c3d4da2e","tid":612884,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"唔算偷偷啦"},{"pid":"ac0fb95d0538cc00c5283ddbcb1cfe2ba98a9bdc","tid":612884,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"有咩驚訝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你用佢啲product有記錄好出奇？"},{"pid":"ad4cb409bb884994c8165acc9d8dc3b932874640","tid":612884,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"90% AV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ed401f159fde077094190b0bf9e47641f46963","tid":612884,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b72a5ef09298b1d22e29cdbf5bb9834671bb04e6","tid":612884,"uid":116688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"想搵返以前睇過嘅AV"},{"pid":"4a2bde7f74b60ba069e2d047405d3019025011db","tid":612884,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b72a5ef09298b1d22e29cdbf5bb9834671bb04e6","tid":612884,"uid":116688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"想搵返以前睇過嘅AV"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2